<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #5c6bc0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #666;
        }
        .reset-code {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            color: #333;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #5c6bc0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #5c6bc0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{user.name}},</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you did not make this request, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Use the code below to reset your password:</p>
            <div class="reset-code">{{token}}</div>
            <p>This password reset code will expire in 30 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@authify.com">contact us</a>. We're happy to help!</p>
            <p>Thanks,<br>The Authify Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; Authify. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
